ns":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[4509,1420],"id":"633f1e1a-3928-4f17-b80e-1e9352cc03d2","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"subject":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage ","bodyContent":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","toRecipients":"={{ $json.email || 'ops@company.com' }}","additionalFields":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.microsoftOutlook","typeVersion":2,"position":[4833,1420],"id":"51b08f32-fadd-4ead-b7c4-34a9fe3b20ef","name":"Escalate Failure to Outlook","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Receive Inbound Webhook\n\nEntry point: listens for POST calls on `/wf06888-document`. Use the TEST url while building, switch callers to the PRODUCTION url after publishing.\n\nNext: Read Recent from Google Drive","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"9705d148-fc25-5d1f-bdde-0673d558a66c","name":"Note: Receive Inbound Webhook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Read Recent from Google Drive\n\ngoogleDrive — `fileFolder` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Newest First · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"905dacb6-7ed3-4a10-bb55-58e94737bf60","name":"Note: Read Recent from Google Drive"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Trim to Digest Size","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"1e07c119-f1d7-6dfd-fd49-c6f0c0878fcb","name":"Note: Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Trim to Digest Size\n\nCaps the stream at 15 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Summarize Content (AI)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"e3ad3598-a638-f414-35cf-ada096439481","name":"Note: Trim to Digest Size"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Content (AI)\n\nMap-reduce summarization chain — handles long content without blowing the context window.\n\nPorts: ①→ Post Digest to Outlook, Post Digest to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"6a6e14ee-946c-b26d-0ea9-89e80dd369ea","name":"Note: Summarize Content (AI)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Groq Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `llama-3.3-70b-versatile`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Summarize Content (AI)** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 Groq API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,1090],"id":"ed12638e-d962-a63b-cd97-edbd69bd1f6f","name":"Note: Groq Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Post Digest to Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Confirm All Sends · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1533,220],"id":"31f19ffc-ec61-9da0-4ac2-8b5aafedd794","name":"Note: Post Digest to Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Post Digest to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Confirm All Sends · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1857,730],"id":"3cf910d1-0f9c-5cfa-4d04-33aba1d8f2db","name":"Note: Post Digest to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Confirm All Sends\n\nRejoins 2 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Archive Digest in Google Sheets","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2505,520],"id":"4e51ca68-cdab-e4a3-47e2-f02668f1ff08","name":"Note: Confirm All Sends"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Digest in Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Save Execution Metadata · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3477,520],"id":"05ea7eaf-6dd5-eaa7-269d-1de9b64fc9d7","name":"Note: Archive Digest in Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty title","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,520],"id":"b0496b62-6042-b8c2-65f7-90816dfafd65","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty title\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4125,520],"id":"5c7b0192-6e54-4cb7-2d47-1a90122addd9","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty title"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4449,520],"id":"5db47f6e-c838-5805-f5d7-f327500382a2","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4773,520],"id":"482714f1-7951-8035-d141-e776a2975015","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5097,520],"id":"2e4aa35d-aade-3204-25cf-49f2411f2788","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Outlook","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4449,1540],"id":"490033ab-1ea3-ea0c-d232-773deffe4fd4","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4773,1540],"id":"7015c003-e7c1-500a-09ea-9ae48690fe9f","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Distill meeting notes with Google Drive and Outlook\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nDistill meeting notes with Google Drive and Outlook. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual q&a is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Read Recent from Google Drive → Newest First → Trim to Digest Size → Summarize Content (AI) → Post Digest to Outlook → Confirm All Sends → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating q&a in ai\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Scales without extra headcount\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Groq API key; Microsoft OAuth2; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"121bf931-6d57-32c2-0194-0bf25179c631","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-320],"id":"1ae5e79b-89be-abd1-16c9-f29537518037","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-320],"id":"bcd1e953-6185-d6f1-dd5b-a5d3546a585f","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-320],"id":"ba9d0e42-1c20-6212-ab78-5132665c04ec","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your q&a process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-320],"id":"c81c6aa1-da6b-791a-3cd7-55280c05f165","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Read Recent from Google Drive","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Read Recent from Google Drive":{"main":[[{"node":"Newest First","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Trim to Digest Size","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Trim to Digest Size":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Content (AI)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Groq Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Summarize Content (AI)","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Summarize Content (AI)":{"main":[[{"node":"Post Digest to Outlook","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Post Digest to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Post Digest to Outlook":{"main":[[{"node":"Confirm All Sends","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Post Digest to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Confirm All Sends","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Confirm All Sends":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Digest in Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Digest in Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty title","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty title":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Outlook","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"910231a0-2f6a-45f0-8f7a-aade9c122f0e","id":"FDX06888"}